{"tid":845483,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麗閣選區：遇前黨友「鎅票」？　馮檢基：比以往鎅得「更深更痛」","createTime":"2018-10-02T16:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T09:16:07.000Z","uid":78519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5dfd14428e9dbcced042cb33e8453cff83c035cf","tid":845483,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20151122/s00001/1448160631060_AC58259C9A76880B7F4BE264E55E30FC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20151122%2Fs00001%2F1448160631060_AC58259C9A76880B7F4BE264E55E30FC.jpg&h=414cee8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之1 - 民協馮檢基今早到其參選的深水埗麗閣邨選區拉票。（渠贇攝）<br />\n<br />\n民協唯一立法會議員馮檢基出選深水埗麗閣邨選區，馮今早站在投票站外，與前來投票站前的選民揮手，但因投票站外屬禁止拉票區，他沒有攜帶任何宣傳物品。有身穿校服的中學生投票後與他合照。馮檢基指，11時前是老人家投票高峰期，自己要把握時機。<br />\n<br />\n馮檢基承認，今次選舉是他自2003年當選當區區議員起選情最嚴峻的一次。他說，前來「鎅票」的前民協成員黃仲棋，票源完全與他重疊，比以往鎅得「更深更痛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20151122/s00001/1448160735674_C11D0075657B9F72E66520FB77B27DEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20151122%2Fs00001%2F1448160735674_C11D0075657B9F72E66520FB77B27DEC.jpg&h=03700c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之2 - 有市民與馮檢基(右)合照。（渠贇攝）<br />\n<br />\n他指，無論工聯會對手陳穎欣或黃仲棋今次都有心思部署，勢要「搣走馮檢基」，競爭比以往強很多。他暫不評估勝選，但承認支持度或有變化，可能長者會因對方物質資源影響而轉態支持對手。<br />\n<br />\n馮檢基又強調希望用政績取勝，花了5年時間令深水埗烏鴉數量驟減，又解決區內蚊患鼠患問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151122/s00001/1448160821568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151122%2Fs00001%2F1448160821568&d=RqU6pVPmSc1SWWoYufi87Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7c9e3508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151122%2Fs00001%2F1448160821568&h=518cc77f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151122/s00001/1448160821568</a>"},{"pid":"9bf7c40724627a4fa0435314c31760b5d1731e00","tid":845483,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3971c2c0f0b51d0dcdbc7a563119d6ec0638f37f","tid":845483,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"樓主想帶出啲乜？"},{"pid":"1e20d16b4eaff3defdeb86130256562a4706ba31","tid":845483,"uid":78519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:50.000Z","msg":"我係戥黃仲祺可惜姐<br />\n佢參選被人話鎅票！"},{"pid":"5164bbf53409f6a5957db8cbec44150563a6e9c1","tid":845483,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"互界啫"}]}